585
00:34:22,420 --> 00:34:24,220
It's a good opportunity to buy
some new things for the mansion.

586
00:34:24,940 --> 00:34:25,700
Besides,

587
00:34:25,780 --> 00:34:27,660
Her Highness has been working hard
on the case lately.

588
00:34:27,940 --> 00:34:29,220
What's wrong with her eating a bit more
to replenish her energy?

589
00:34:29,940 --> 00:34:31,540
It could cause inner heat.

590
00:34:31,540 --> 00:34:32,620
Just shut up.

591
00:34:33,380 --> 00:34:35,500
Take a look at the top-tier rouge.

592
00:34:35,500 --> 00:34:36,900
