595
00:34:38,900 --> 00:34:40,060
Take a look at the top-tier rouge.

596
00:34:40,740 --> 00:34:41,980
Sir, have a look.

597
00:34:42,020 --> 00:34:44,060
This finest rouge beautifies
and nourishes the skin.

598
00:34:44,460 --> 00:34:45,540
Take a look.
It will beautify and nourish your skin.

599
00:34:45,540 --> 00:34:47,100
