600
00:34:47,100 --> 00:34:48,540
Are these the newest styles
that haven't been seen before?

601
00:34:48,540 --> 00:34:49,620
Of course, sir.

602
00:34:49,620 --> 00:34:51,580
This is the best rouge ever known.

603
00:34:51,580 --> 00:34:52,460
Buying one for your wife

604
00:34:52,460 --> 00:34:53,900
