609
00:35:07,220 --> 00:35:08,460
There's an organization

610
00:35:08,460 --> 00:35:10,260
that likes to find such people
and train them to become assassins.

611
00:35:10,820 --> 00:35:11,740
They may look like children,

612
00:35:11,900 --> 00:35:13,140
which easily lowers people's guard.

613
00:35:14,340 --> 00:35:15,540
But in strength and skill,

614
00:35:15,540 --> 00:35:17,260
they are fully capable adults.

615
00:35:17,860 --> 00:35:18,860
They are so evil.

616
00:35:19,620 --> 00:35:20,940
