617
00:35:21,540 --> 00:35:23,140
Hurry back to the Inspectorate Office
and prepare for support.

618
00:35:24,260 --> 00:35:24,940
Yes, sir.

619
00:35:25,860 --> 00:35:26,500
Ya.

620
00:35:27,620 --> 00:35:29,660
You need to pay close attention
