635
00:36:09,420 --> 00:36:11,420
Don't worry, I'll protect myself.

636
00:36:16,220 --> 00:36:17,060
So,

637
00:36:17,460 --> 00:36:18,900
I'll figure out who did this.

638
00:36:24,980 --> 00:36:25,620
