645
00:37:16,940 --> 00:37:17,500
Here.

646
00:37:20,900 --> 00:37:21,780
Alright, that's enough.

647
00:37:22,700 --> 00:37:23,780
You should also have some.

648
00:37:24,140 --> 00:37:25,140
I'll manage on my own.

649
00:37:26,260 --> 00:37:27,300
Really, I can handle it myself.

650
00:37:27,300 --> 00:37:28,020
How are you going
to manage by yourself?

651
00:37:28,020 --> 00:37:29,180
You couldn't even
pick things up just now.

652
00:37:30,420 --> 00:37:31,540
Don't starve yourself.

653
00:37:31,620 --> 00:37:32,380
I'm fine.

654
00:37:34,100 --> 00:37:34,860
Your Highness.

655
00:37:39,420 --> 00:37:40,540
