656
00:37:42,580 --> 00:37:44,060
Go ahead and see her.
I can manage on my own.

657
00:37:45,540 --> 00:37:46,900
If I leave, how will you eat the food?

658
00:37:47,420 --> 00:37:48,140
Don't be stubborn.

659
00:37:49,660 --> 00:37:50,540
Ask Ya to wait a bit.

660
00:37:50,540 --> 00:37:51,580
I'll go to see her
after I finish eating.

661
00:37:54,580 --> 00:37:55,260
Yes, Your Highness.

662
00:37:56,580 --> 00:37:57,220
Open your mouth.

663
00:38:05,740 --> 00:38:08,580
Actually, being injured like this
could be quite good.

664
00:38:13,300 --> 00:38:15,260
I mean, the dish tastes really good.

665
00:38:15,740 --> 00:38:16,460
Try it.

666
00:38:20,940 --> 00:38:21,700
Your Highness.

667
00:38:22,900 --> 00:38:24,860
Your Highness, how's the Prince Consort?

668
00:38:24,980 --> 00:38:25,940
Is he seriously injured?

669
00:38:26,460 --> 00:38:27,220
Not that serious.

670
00:38:28,100 --> 00:38:29,420
Why are you here so late then?

671
00:38:29,580 --> 00:38:30,900
It's inconvenient for him
to have soup on his own.

672
00:38:32,620 --> 00:38:33,740
I'm getting

673
00:38:34,100 --> 00:38:35,860
a bit jealous of him.

674
00:38:38,780 --> 00:38:39,860
Let's get to the point.

675
00:38:41,460 --> 00:38:44,100
Is the knife that injured
the Prince Consort poisoned?

676
00:38:47,300 --> 00:38:48,900
They just want to warn me

677
00:38:49,380 --> 00:38:51,580
rather than completely ruin
our relationship.

678
00:38:53,420 --> 00:38:54,460
At this point,

679
00:38:54,540 --> 00:38:56,660
all they're asking for is a way out.

680
00:38:57,300 --> 00:39:00,020
They are already targeting
the Prince Consort as a mere warning.

681
00:39:00,580 --> 00:39:01,780
If they're serious,

682
00:39:02,100 --> 00:39:04,500
then today, the Prince Consort might...

683
00:39:06,540 --> 00:39:07,540
What are you trying to say?

684
00:39:08,620 --> 00:39:10,590
Your Highness,
I'm afraid being too rigid

685
00:39:10,590 --> 00:39:11,700
will lead to a downfall.

686
00:39:12,260 --> 00:39:13,500
Perhaps we should take a step back.

687
00:39:18,900 --> 00:39:20,180
If they hadn't taken action,

688
00:39:21,180 --> 00:39:23,060
I might have spared them.

689
00:39:25,460 --> 00:39:26,300
But now...

690
00:39:28,100 --> 00:39:29,140
unless I'm dead,

691
00:39:29,980 --> 00:39:31,420
it will be them who die.

692
00:39:31,620 --> 00:39:33,580
What do you plan to do?

693
00:39:39,300 --> 00:39:41,620
They're in the dark
while we're in the open.

694
00:39:42,740 --> 00:39:43,980
We can't keep up like this.

695
00:39:46,620 --> 00:39:47,500
You go investigate first.

696
00:39:47,780 --> 00:39:49,020
If you can't find anything,

697
00:39:49,780 --> 00:39:51,020
we'll lure the enemy in

698
00:39:51,220 --> 00:39:52,460
and then trap them.

699
00:39:52,940 --> 00:39:53,740
What will we use as bait?

700
00:39:57,660 --> 00:39:58,300
Me.

701
00:40:00,100 --> 00:40:00,740
Slowly.

702
00:40:05,100 --> 00:40:06,340
I often wonder...

703
00:40:08,540 --> 00:40:11,380
what you would be like as a wife.

704
00:40:14,300 --> 00:40:17,220
You'd probably be a good wife
and a loving mother.

705
00:40:18,740 --> 00:40:21,460
Although you appear decisive
on the surface,

706
00:40:22,260 --> 00:40:23,500
you are also gentle.

707
00:40:26,500 --> 00:40:28,020
Being taken care of by you
for this while

708
00:40:28,340 --> 00:40:32,140
makes me feel at home.

709
00:40:44,540 --> 00:40:45,700
I might leave the capital...

710
00:40:47,420 --> 00:40:48,940
