711
00:40:52,060 --> 00:40:52,860
Leave the capital?

712
00:40:55,460 --> 00:40:56,500
There have been too many things going on

713
00:40:56,500 --> 00:40:57,420
at the Inspectorate Office lately.

714
00:40:57,420 --> 00:40:59,100
I need to get out and clear my mind.

715
00:41:01,060 --> 00:41:02,660
You're going out
without taking me with you?

716
00:41:03,820 --> 00:41:05,700
You're injured.
You should stay home and rest.

717
00:41:06,500 --> 00:41:07,780
This injury is nothing.

718
00:41:08,020 --> 00:41:08,820
No, you can't...

719
00:41:08,820 --> 00:41:09,540
Where are you planning to go?

720
00:41:11,340 --> 00:41:12,420
I haven't decided yet.

721
00:41:13,180 --> 00:41:16,340
No worries.
I'll help you think about it.

722
00:41:20,300 --> 00:41:22,540
I need to find a place
where it's easy to ambush them.

723
00:41:26,940 --> 00:41:27,620
Young Master.

724
00:41:30,420 --> 00:41:31,180
I found it.

725
00:41:32,580 --> 00:41:33,420
Make some space.

726
00:41:36,060 --> 00:41:36,780
What place is it?

727
00:41:39,100 --> 00:41:40,300
Butterfly Gorge.

728
00:41:42,380 --> 00:41:44,780
There is a river in the gorge
and flowers on the shore.

729
00:41:44,940 --> 00:41:46,020
